creator: RaceID
descriptionHtml:
Looking for your next challenge? Search here! Whether it’s running, biking, swimming, adventure racing or any other endurance sport, you will find your next challenge on RaceID.
RaceID is the number one meeting place for anyone who loves endurance races. Here, you can collect everything about your race journey in one place; your results, register for races and challenge your friends. Your entire race journey. All in one place.
You will love RaceID because you can:
- Join events all over the world;
- Get all the information you need about the upcoming events;
- Register together with your friends as a group or a team;
- Participate in virtual events to enjoy racing even if it’s currently not possible for you to join real-life events;
- Follow your friends to see in which races they participate;
- Compare your achievements to the racers you follow;
- Stay up to date on news from the race organisers you follow.
descriptionShort: RaceID is the number one meeting place for anyone who loves endurance races.
